      <div class="bar-row"><div class="bar-label">Developing (25–44%)</div><div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:42.9%;background:#e67e22;color:#fff">421</div></div><div class="bar-val">42.9%</div></div>
      <div class="bar-row"><div class="bar-label">Moderate (45–64%)</div><div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:26.2%;background:#2980b9;color:#fff">257</div></div><div class="bar-val">26.2%</div></div>
      <div class="bar-row"><div class="bar-label">Strong (65%+)</div><div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:10.6%;background:#27ae60;color:#fff">104</div></div><div class="bar-val">10.6%</div></div>
      <div style="margin-top:12px;font-size:11px;color:#7f8ea3">63.3% of students below 45% readiness — primary upsell pool</div>
    </div>
    <div class="ccard">
      <h3>Subject accuracy (avg across all students)</h3>
      <div class="bar-row"><div class="bar-label">Verbal Reasoning</div><div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:65.3%;background:#27ae60;color:#fff">65.3%</div></div><div class="bar-val">65.3%</div></div>
      <div class="bar-row"><div class="bar-label">English</div><div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:45.9%;background:#2980b9;color:#fff">45.9%</div></div><div class="bar-val">45.9%</div></div>
      <div class="bar-row"><div class="bar-label">Quant Aptitude</div><div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:36.9%;background:#e74c3c;color:#fff">36.9%</div></div><div class="bar-val">36.9%</div></div>
      <div style="margin-top:16px">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom:12px">Accuracy by cohort</h3>
        <div class="bar-row"><div class="bar-label" style="width:90px">Strong</div><div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:71.4%;background:#27ae60;color:#fff">71.4%</div></div></div>
        <div class="bar-row"><div class="bar-label" style="width:90px">Moderate</div><div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:58.7%;background:#2980b9;color:#fff">58.7%</div></div></div>
        <div class="bar-row"><div class="bar-label" style="width:90px">Developing</div><div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:42.8%;background:#e67e22;color:#fff">42.8%</div></div></div>
        <div class="bar-row"><div class="bar-label" style="width:90px">Critical</div><div class="bar-bg"><div class="bar-fill" style="width:22.9%;background:#e74c3c;color:#fff">22.9%</div></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="chart-grid">
    <div class="ccard">
      <h3>Top 8 weak chapters</h3>
